\c 2
\s Vanakomana vane gumi navaviri vaIsraeri, navana vavo
\p
\v 1 Ndivo vanakomana vaIsraeri: Rubheni, naSimioni, naRevhi, naJudha, naIsaskari naZebhuruni,
\v 2 naDhani, naJosefa naBhenjamini, naNafutari, naGadhi, naAsheri.
\p
\v 3 Vanakomana vaJudha: Eri, naOnani, naShera; vanakomana ava vatatu akavaberekerwa naBhatishua muKenani. Asi Eri, mwana wedangwe waJudha, akange ari munhu akaipa pamberi paJehovha, akamuuraya.
\p
\v 4 Tamari mukadzi womwana wake, akamuberekera Perezi naZera. Vanakomana vese vaJudha vakange vari vashanu.
\v 5 Vanakomana vaPerezi: Hezironi naHamuri.
\v 6 Vanakomana vaZera: Zimiri, naEtani, naHemani, naKarikori, naDhara; vese vari vashanu.
\p
\v 7 Vanakomana vaKarimi: Akari, mutambudzi waIsraeri, wakatadza pachinhu chakange chakayeriswa.
\v 8 Vanakomana vaEtani: Azara.
\p
\v 9 Vanakomanawo vaHezironi, vaakaberekerwa: Jerameeri, naRami, naKerubhai.
\v 10 Rami akabereka Aminadhabhu, Aminadhabhu akabereka
\v 11 Naashoni, muchinda wavana vaJudha; Naashoni akabereka Sarima, Sarima akabereka Bhowasi;
\v 12 Bhowasi akabereka Obhedhi, Obhedhi akabereka Jese;
\v 13 Jese akabereka mwana wake wedangwe Eriabhi, tevere Abhinadhabhu wechipiri, naShimea wechitatu;
\v 14 naNetaneri wechina, naRadhai weshanu;
\v 15 naOzemi wetanhatu, naDhavhidhi wechinomwe.
\v 16 Hanzvadzi dzavo dzaiva Zeruya naAbhigairi. Vanakomana vaZeruya: Abhishai, naJoabhu, naAsaheri, vatatu.
\v 17 Abhigairi akabereka Amasa; baba vaAmasa vaiva Jeteri muIshimaeri.
\p
\v 18 Karebhu mwanakomana waHezironi akaberekerwa vana nomukadzi wake Azubha, uye naJerioti; ava ndivo vaiva vanakomana vake: Jesheri, naShobhabhi, naAridhoni.
\v 19 Azubha akafa, Karebhu akawana Efurati, wakamuberekera Huri.
\p
\v 20 Huri akabereka Uri, Uri akabereka Bhezari.
\v 21 Shure kwaizvozvo Hezironi akapinda kumukunda waMakiri baba vaGiriyadhi, waakawana ava wemakore makumi matanhatu; iye akamuberekera Segubhi.
\v 22 Segubhi akabereka Jairi, akange ana maguta ana makumi maviri namatatu panyika yeGiriyadhi.
\p
\v 23 Geshuri naArami vakatorera vaJairi maguta avo, pamwechete neKenati nemisha yaro, maguta ana makumi matanhatu. Ava vese vaiva vanakomana vaMakiri baba vaGiriyadhi.
\v 24 Zvino Hezironi akati afa paKarebhiefirata, Abhija mukadzi waHezironi akamuberekera Ashuri baba vaTekoa.
\p
\v 25 Vanakomana vaJerameeri, mwanakomana wedangwe waHezironi, vaiva, Rami wedangwe, naBhuna, naOreni, naOzemi, naAhija.
\v 26 Zvino Jerameeri akange anomumwe mukadzi, ainzi Atara; iye akange ari mai vaOnami.
\v 27 Vanakomana vaRami, wedangwe waJerameeri, vaiva Maazi, naJamini, naEkeri.
\p
\v 28 Vanakomana vaOnami vaiva Shamai, naJadha. Vanakomana vaShamai: Nadhabhi naAbhishuri.
\p
\v 29 Zita romukadzi waAbhishuri raiva Abhihairi; iye akamuberekera Abhani, naMoridhi.
\v 30 Vanakomana vaNadhabhi: Seredhi, naApaimi; asi Seredhi akafa asina vana.
\v 31 Vanakomana vaApaimi: Ishi. Vanakomana vaIshi: Sheshani. Vanakomana vaSheshani: Arai.
\p
\v 32 Vanakomana vaJadha, munin'ina waShamai: Jeteri, naJonatani; Jeteri akafa asina vana.
\p
\v 33 Vanakomana vaJonatani: Pereti naZaza. Ndivo vaiva vanakomana vaJerameeri.
\p
\v 34 Zvino Sheshani akange asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana. Sheshani akange ano muranda, muEgipita, ainzi Jara.
\v 35 Sheshani akapa Jara muranda wake mukunda wake ave mukadzi wake; iye akamuberekera Atai.
\v 36 Atai akabereka Natani, Natani akabereka Zabhadhi;
\v 37 Zabhadhi akabereka Efirari, Efirari akabereka Obhedhi;
\v 38 Obhedhi akabereka Jehu, Jehu akabereka Azaria;
\v 39 Azaria akabereka Herezi, Herezi akabereka Ereasa;
\v 40 Ereasa akabereka Sisimai, Sisimai akabereka Sharumi;
\v 41 Sharumi akabereka Jekamia, Jekamia akabereka Erishama.
\p
\v 42 Vanakomana vaKarebhu munin'ina waJerameeri, vaiva Mesha dangwe rake, akange ari baba vaZifi; navanakomana vaMaresha baba vaHebhuroni.
\v 43 Vanakomana vaHebhuroni: Kora, naTapua, naRekemi, naShema.
\v 44 Shema akabereka Rahami, baba vaJorikeami; Rekemi akabereka Shamai.
\v 45 Mwanakomana waShamai akange ari Maoni; Maoni akange ari baba vaBhetizuri.
\p
\v 46 Efa murongo waKarebhu, akabereka Harani, naMoza, naGazezi; Harami akabereka Gazezi.
\p
\v 47 Vanakomana vaJadha: Regemi, naJotamu, naGeshani, naPereti, naEfa, naShaafi.
\v 48 Maaka, murongo waKarebhu, akabereka Shebheri naTirihana.
\p
\v 49 Iye akaberekawo Shaafi baba vaMadhimana, Shevha baba vaMakibhena, nababa vaGibhiya; mukunda waKarebhu akange ari Akisa.
\p
\v 50 Ndivo vanakomana vaKarebhu: Mwanakomana waHuri, wedangwe waEfurati: Shobhari baba vaKiriati-jearimi;
\v 51 Sarima baba vaBheterehemu, Harefi baba vaBhetigadheri.
\v 52 Shobhari baba vaKiriati-jearimi akange ana vanakomana: Haroe, nehafu yorudzi rwavaMenuhoti.
\p
\v 53 Marudzi aKiriati-jearimi: Valtiri, navaPuti, navaShumati, navaMishirai; kwavari ndiko kwakabva vaZorati navaEshitaori.
\p
\v 54 Vanakomana vaSarima: Bheterehemu, navaNetofati, Atirotibhetijoabhi, nehafu yorudzi rwavaManahati, navaZori.
\p
\v 55 Uye marudzi avanyori, aigara paJabhezi: VaTirati, vaShimeati, navaSukati. Ndivo vaKeni vakabva kuna Hamati baba veimba yaRekabhi.
